title: DDFP 377: NFC North & top young QBs
itunes:title: DDFP 377: NFC North & top young QBs
description:
Shek is joined by Handsome Hank, Ike Taylor and Maurice Jones-Drew to dive deep into the latest news including Steve Smith’s retirement and Geno Smith’s injury. MJD then lists his top signal callers from the past two drafts. Finally, the guys wrap up the show by previewing the NFC North.
